                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Mediocre but regular</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red (vivid vermilion)</seg>
                        <date>18th century</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ትር/ትርጓ</abbr> for <expan>ትርጓሜ </expan> (<locus target="#17vb">17vb</locus>, 19vb, 27va)</item>
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ን/ንባ</abbr> for <expan>ንባብ ዘጳውሎስ </expan> (e.g., <locus target="#35ra">35ra</locus>, 35vb, 36rb)</item>
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ፍ/ፍካ</abbr> for <expan>ፍካሬ ዘቄርሎስ </expan> (e.g., <locus target="#35ra">35ra</locus>, 35va, 36ra)</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the donor; incipit of Texts I
                           and III; a few lines on the incipit page of Text II, alternating with
                           black lines; two initial lines of each section of Texts II;
                           abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic
                           numerals; some words like nǝgbaʾke ḫaba (fol. 4ra), yǝbe (fol. 6rb), kǝfl
                           (e.g., fols. 7vb, 8rb, 9ra), tǝrgʷāme (fol. 20vb), fǝkkāre (fols.
                           37vb).</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#146vb">f. 146vb</locus>
                           <desc type="DonationNote">Donation note.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ ማርያም፡
                              ለደብረ፡ ዳሞ፡ ኢትርስኡኒ፡ በጊዜ፡ ጸሎት፡ ወቊርባን፡ ዘሰረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡፡</q>
                           <note> The note mentions ʾabuna Gabra Māryām as the
                              donor. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1"><desc>- The title of the work, መጽሃፈ ቄርሎስ, is written in black
                           paint on <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>.</desc>  </item>
                        <item xml:id="e2"><desc> - The monastery’s internal
                           registry number, 292, is written on <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>. </desc> </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3"><desc>A crude recent note mentioning ʾabbā Kidāna Māryām, ʾabbā Za-Walda and
                           Dabra Damo on <locus target="#2r">2r</locus>.  </desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e4"><desc>Tamallas-sign
                           indicating the place where the omissions, written in the margins, belong:
                           fols 7ra, 34va, 52ra, 111ra. </desc> </item>
                        <item xml:id="e5"><desc>Corrections, biblical references,
                           glosses and commentaries in the margins of each fol. of Text II.</desc>  </item>
                        <item xml:id="e6">
                           <desc>Corrections written interlineally: e.g., <locus target="#7rb">7rb</locus>, 10rb, 14rb, 25ra, 47vb.</desc>  </item>
                        <item xml:id="e7">
                           <desc> Corrections written over
                           erasures: e.g., <locus target="#9ra">9ra</locus>, 9vb, 13ra, 16ra, 17ra,
                           17vb, 19va, 22ra, 92va, 122va. </desc> </item>
                        <item xml:id="e8"><desc> Immediate corrections marked by
                           thin lines above and below words: <locus target="#49ra">49ra</locus>,
                           69ra.</desc> </item>
                        <item xml:id="e9">
                           <desc>Spaces filed by three horizontal thin lines: e.g., <locus target="#9rb">9rb</locus>, 10vb, 22va-b, 23ra, 24ra-va, 28vb, 39vb.
                           </desc>  </item>
                        <item xml:id="e10">
                           <desc>The word መጽሃፈ is written in black paint on the outer face of the
                           front board.</desc></item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
